S3 method for providing summary for the shorts_mixed_model object

# S3 method for shorts_mixed_model
summary(object, ...)

Arguments

object

shorts_mixed_model object
...

Not used

Examples

data("split_times")

mixed_model <- mixed_model_using_splits(
  data = split_times,
  distance = "distance",
  time = "time",
  athlete = "athlete"
)

summary(mixed_model)
